---
title: Blog
layout: retro-page.njk
permalink: /blog/index.html
windowLabel: SAVE_FILES
kicker: Archive / Writing
description: Notes on building, psychology, fear, and whatever else is currently taking up too much RAM.
---

<div class="post-list">
  {% for post in collections.post | reverse %}
    <a class="save-slot" href="{{ post.url }}">
      <span class="slot-number">{% if loop.index < 10 %}0{% endif %}{{ loop.index }}</span>
      <span class="slot-copy">
        <h2>{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
        <p>{{ post.data.summary }}</p>
      </span>
      <time class="slot-date" datetime="{{ post.data.machineDate }}">{{ post.data.displayDate }}</time>
    </a>
  {% else %}
    <p class="empty-state">NO SAVE FILES FOUND... YET.</p>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
